{"tha-ap43:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap43:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap43:0.3":"1 Bhagineyyupalittheraapadana ","tha-ap43:1.1":"“Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap43:1.2":"parivuto lokanayako; ","tha-ap43:1.3":"Vivekamanuyutto so, ","tha-ap43:1.4":"gacchate patisallitum. ","tha-ap43:2.1":"Ajinena nivatthoham, ","tha-ap43:2.2":"tidandaparidharako; ","tha-ap43:2.3":"Bhikkhusanghaparibyulham, ","tha-ap43:2.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap43:3.1":"Ekamsam ajinam katva, ","tha-ap43:3.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap43:3.3":"Sambuddham abhivadetva, ","tha-ap43:3.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap43:4.1":"Yathandaja ca samseda, ","tha-ap43:4.2":"opapati jalabuja; ","tha-ap43:4.3":"Kakadipakkhino sabbe, ","tha-ap43:4.4":"antalikkhacara sada. ","tha-ap43:5.1":"‘Ye keci panabhutatthi, ","tha-ap43:5.2":"sannino va asannino; ","tha-ap43:5.3":"Sabbe te tava nanamhi, ","tha-ap43:5.4":"anto honti samogadha. ","tha-ap43:6.1":"Gandha ca pabbateyya ye, ","tha-ap43:6.2":"himavantanaguttame; ","tha-ap43:6.3":"Sabbe te tava silamhi, ","tha-ap43:6.4":"kalayapi na yujjare. ","tha-ap43:7.1":"Mohandhakarapakkhando, ","tha-ap43:7.2":"ayam loko sadevako; ","tha-ap43:7.3":"Tava nanamhi jotante, ","tha-ap43:7.4":"andhakara vidhamsita. ","tha-ap43:8.1":"Yatha atthangate suriye, ","tha-ap43:8.2":"honti satta tamogata; ","tha-ap43:8.3":"Evam buddhe anuppanne, ","tha-ap43:8.4":"hoti loko tamogato. ","tha-ap43:9.1":"Yathodayanto adicco, ","tha-ap43:9.2":"vinodeti tamam sada; ","tha-ap43:9.3":"Tatheva tvam buddhasettha, ","tha-ap43:9.4":"viddhamsesi tamam sada. ","tha-ap43:10.1":"Padhanapahitattosi, ","tha-ap43:10.2":"buddho loke sadevake; ","tha-ap43:10.3":"Tava kammabhiraddhena, ","tha-ap43:10.4":"tosesi janatam bahum’. ","tha-ap43:11.1":"Tam sabbam anumoditva, ","tha-ap43:11.2":"padumuttaro mahamuni; ","tha-ap43:11.3":"Nabham abbhuggami dhiro, ","tha-ap43:11.4":"hamsarajava ambare. ","tha-ap43:12.1":"Abbhuggantvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap43:12.2":"mahesi padumuttaro; ","tha-ap43:12.3":"Antalikkhe thito sattha, ","tha-ap43:12.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap43:13.1":"Yenidam thavitam nanam, ","tha-ap43:13.2":"opammehi samayutam; ","tha-ap43:13.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap43:13.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap43:14.1":"‘Attharasanca khattum so, ","tha-ap43:14.2":"devaraja bhavissati; ","tha-ap43:14.3":"Pathabya rajjam tisatam, ","tha-ap43:14.4":"vasudham avasissati. ","tha-ap43:15.1":"Pancavisatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap43:15.2":"cakkavatti bhavissati; ","tha-ap43:15.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap43:15.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap43:16.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap43:16.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap43:16.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap43:16.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap43:17.1":"Tusita hi cavitvana, ","tha-ap43:17.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap43:17.3":"Hinova jatiya santo, ","tha-ap43:17.4":"upali nama hessati. ","tha-ap43:18.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap43:18.2":"virajetvana papakam; ","tha-ap43:18.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap43:18.4":"nibbayissatinasavo. ","tha-ap43:19.1":"Tuttho ca gotamo buddho, ","tha-ap43:19.2":"sakyaputto mahayaso; ","tha-ap43:19.3":"Vinayadhigatam tassa, ","tha-ap43:19.4":"etadagge thapessati’. ","tha-ap43:20.1":"Saddhayaham pabbajito, ","tha-ap43:20.2":"katakicco anasavo; ","tha-ap43:20.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap43:20.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap43:21.1":"Bhagava canukampi mam, ","tha-ap43:21.2":"vinayeham visarado; ","tha-ap43:21.3":"Sakakammabhiraddho ca, ","tha-ap43:21.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap43:22.1":"Samvuto patimokkhamhi, ","tha-ap43:22.2":"indriyesu ca pancasu; ","tha-ap43:22.3":"Dharemi vinayam sabbam, ","tha-ap43:22.4":"kevalam ratanakaram. ","tha-ap43:23.1":"Mamanca gunamannaya, ","tha-ap43:23.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap43:23.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap43:23.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap43:24.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap43:24.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap43:24.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap43:24.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap43:25.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma upali thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap43:26.1":"Bhagineyyupalittherassapadanam pathamam. "}